{
  "id": "2024-09-26",
  "title": "September 26th, 2024",
  "body": [
    {
      "color": "blue",
      "text": [
        "Before I met you,",
        "mountain streams fell",
        "cold down pine tree slopes",
        "into an abyssal ocean."
      ]
    },
    {
      "color": "",
      "text": [
        "Glaciers evolved with seasons,",
        "yet mountains remained",
        "forever crowned in snow",
        "and icy clouds."
      ]
    },
    {
      "color": "",
      "text": [
        "Then two primrose stars appeared,",
        "scattering the night's darkness and",
        "illuminating my midnight world",
        "with rays of lemon and white."
      ]
    },
    {
      "color": "",
      "text": [
        "Mountain springs burst",
        "forth with warmth and joy,",
        "and sunbeams danced in unison",
        "with their careless currents."
      ]
    },
    {
      "color": "",
      "text": [
        "From there new streams flowed",
        "like melted candle wax,",
        "and a blue sky dyed them",
        "gently with pastel grace."
      ]
    },
    {
      "color": "",
      "text": [
        "I felt peaceful,",
        "happy,",
        "healthy,",
        "and filled with love."
      ]
    },
    {
      "color": "",
      "text": [
        "Every winter memory became",
        "transient like a fading dream,",
        "as my thoughts filled with",
        "the hopes of mid-May flowers."
      ]
    }
  ]
}
